President Uhuru Kenyatta and Deputy President William Ruto will govern until 2032, Taveta MP Naomi Shaban (pictured) has said. If you don t put your house in order, Uhuru will win his second term before passing the baton to Ruto, who will lead for another two terms, she told opposition leader Raila Odinga. The National Assembly deputy majority leader spoke on Thursday in Taveta town during Mashujaa Day celebrations.